sentence:
We are pleased to have posted after tax operating income of $185 million
for the second quarter even though we increased our provision for the first quarter catastrophes,
particularly the Chilean earthquake.

Our successes included a great start from our new office in Brazil; growing our International books
on attractive accounts, which was aided by some of our major competitors having financial problems;
maintaining a leadership position in the retro property market and the Florida property market;
maintaining our core Casualty Reinsurance clients; starting a new insurance operation to respond to
the future need for our financial institution directors' and officers' liability; and adding a new insurance
program for smaller financial institutions.
